<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>CSS Display Property Demo</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Block element */
    .block-element {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      border: 2px solid #007BFF;
      padding: 10px;
      background-color: #e7f1ff;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Inline element */
    .inline-element {
      display: inline;
      background-color: #d4edda;
      color: #155724;
      padding: 5px;
      border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
    }

    /* Inline-block element */
    .inline-block-element {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 120px;
      height: 80px;
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      color: #856404;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 80px;
      border: 1px solid #ffeeba;
      margin: 10px;
    }

    /* Hidden element */
    .hidden-element {
      display: none;
      background-color: #f8d7da;
      color: #721c24;
      padding: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }

    .note {
      font-style: italic;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>CSS Display Property Demo </h1>

  <div class="block-element">
    <strong>Block Element:</strong> This box takes up the full width of the container and starts on a new line.
  </div>

  <p>
    <strong>Inline Element:</strong> This is an
    <span class="inline-element">inline span</span>
    within a paragraph. It flows with the text and doesnâ€™t break to a new line.
  </p>

  <div>
    <strong>Inline-Block Elements:</strong><br>
    <span class="inline-block-element">Box 1</span>
    <span class="inline-block-element">Box 2</span>
  </div>

  <div class="hidden-element">
    You shouldn't see this element. It has <code>display: none</code>.
  </div>

  <div class="note">
    Note: The hidden element is in the HTML but not rendered on the page due to <code>display: none</code>.
  </div>

</body>
</html>
